      "updated": 1779724256345,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "_> BST,a Binary Tree, is a fundamental  data structure. \n    I may be empty ,if not then all the nodes follows below properties :\n       \n     i)   Every elements have to be unique\n     ii)   Every elements in  the left subtree are smaller than the elemnt in the root \n            of the subtree",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "_> BST,a Binary Tree, is a fundamental  data structure. \n    I may be empty ,if not then all the nodes follows below properties :\n       \n     i)   Every elements have to be unique\n     ii)   Every elements in  the left subtree are smaller than the elemnt in the root \n            of the subtree",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
