      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Algorithm: \n\nstep1 : start at the root node\n\nstep2 : Compare the value with the current node`s value \n\nstep3 : if the value is smaller , move to the left child \n\nstep 4: If the value is grater , move to the right child \n\nstep 5 : Repeat 2-4 , until you find a empty spot\n\nstep 6: Insert the node ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
