      "updated": 1779729211122,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "In summary, if the deleted node is a leaf or has only one child, it is more likely to regain its position\nHowever, if it has two children, the replacement process reshuffles the tree such that the node will \nalmost certainly end up in a different position",
      "fontSize": 26.357038252832712,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "In summary, if the deleted node is a leaf or has only one child, it is more likely to regain its position\nHowever, if it has two children, the replacement process reshuffles the tree such that the node will \nalmost certainly end up in a different position",
